<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.7.10">
<l>tāymaṉam niṉṟiraṅkat taṉiyēneṭu māltuṇaiyā</l>
<l>pōyiṉa pūṅkoṭiyāḷ puṉalālipu kuvareṉṟu</l>
<l>kāyciṉa vēlkaliya ṉoliceytamiḻ mālaipattum</l>
<l>mēviya neñcuṭaiyār tañcamāvatu viṇṇulakē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The refuge of those whose hearts have learned</l>
<l rend="indent">this garland of ten Tamil [verses]</l>
<l>Composed in the words of Kaliyaṉ of the burning, vicious spear,</l>
<l rend="indent">saying ‘they are setting out for Āli of the waters,’</l>
<l>[About] the one like a budding creeper who went on [her] own</l>
<l rend="indent">as the companion of tall Māl,</l>
<l>So that [her] mother’s mind was always distressed,</l>
<l rend="indent">will be the world of heaven.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
